#. type: Title ##
#: faq.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "What is SPDX? {#what-is-spdx}"
msgstr "¿Qué es SPDX? {#what-is-spdx}"

#. type: Plain text
#: faq.md
msgid "SPDX stands for [Software Package Data Exchange](https://spdx.org/). It is a project by the [Linux Foundation](https://www.linuxfoundation.org/) and the rock upon which REUSE is built. SPDX defines a standardized way to share copyright and licensing information between projects and people. Most importantly for REUSE, SPDX maintains the [SPDX License List](https://spdx.org/licenses/), which defines standardized identifiers for a lot of licenses."
msgstr ""
"SPDX siglas de [Software Package Data Exchange](https://spdx.org/). Es un "
"proyecto de la [Linux Foundation](https://www.linuxfoundation.org/) y el "
"pilar sobre el que se construye REUSE. SPDX define una forma normalizada de "
"compartir información sobre derechos de autor y licencias entre proyectos y "
"personas. Lo más importante para REUSE, SPDX mantiene la [SPDX License "
"List](https://spdx.org/licenses/), que define identificadores estandarizados "
"para un montón de licencias."

